17:10.863 --> 17:12.164 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in Britain.

17:12.197 --> 17:14.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
William Brangham takes a deeper
look.

17:14.066 --> 17:18.170 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: As British
officials continue
to piece together who was behind
this attack,

17:18.203 --> 17:22.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and to try to stop another from
occurring,
