relevant tool in
prior terror investigations.

18:53.098 --> 18:55.167 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
R.P. EDDY: It's a massive
difference.

18:55.200 --> 18:59.571 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, they adapted the use of
closed-circuit
televisions much earlier than we
did in the

18:59.605 --> 19:01.573 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
United States in our major
cities.

19:01.607 --> 19:08.213 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And in every terrorist
investigation since
the '80s, CCTVs have been hugely
useful in

19:08.247 --> 19:11.750 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
