was behind it
and wrapping up the cell.

19:11.783 --> 19:17.689 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That and the laws, most of these
things are
children of growing up in the
era of the IRA

19:17.723 --> 19:19.491 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
